room_title: Escape room "Chapter 1: The Doctor's Secret" by Lost Games in Las Vegas

room_description: Dr. Robert Keiling is the head doctor at Solitude Heights Insane Asylum. He is the best there is, but what he does with his talents is questionable. What will you discover here? What is the doctor hiding? Will you find the antidote in time?
